{"tid":2098590,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家辭職是否不智？","createTime":"2020-07-07T14:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T06:46:29.000Z","uid":129836,"like":22,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d2b7c5bd2937db7530c338cd5f81327b35c6a7","tid":2098590,"uid":129836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:57:10.000Z","msg":"依家份工做左一年零八個月<br />\n早幾個月空降左個男上司 面和心不和<br />\n好似磨合極大家都唔係好夾 開始有啲頂唔順<br />\n<br />\n同team有個同事都係因為佢 上個月走咗<br />\n聽佢講見到廿鳩幾份工 仲係未有著落<br />\n我都諗咗幾個月 望住依家失業率咁高真係好卻步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日諗住肺炎好快過 個市好返啲就可以走<br />\n拖下拖下終於到咗頂唔順嘅一刻 肺炎又未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早兩個禮拜老細搵我吹水 話諗住我做夠兩年就升我<br />\n我仲半信半疑緊 覺得佢係驚冇人幫佢做嘢先用呢招氹我<br />\n聽返有幾個同事都係話會升最後都冇升 等下等下就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有幾個月先夠兩年 但係我好似忍唔到咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家辭職 係咪好on9？"},{"pid":"cc61ccf622c7b4837883a37d7810c34cf1695dd9","tid":2098590,"uid":129836,"like":53,"dislike":93,"score":-40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:58:18.000Z","msg":"走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f6f2a9c2bed77cab0864dd3bdb46517c985c3e","tid":2098590,"uid":28668,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:58:23.000Z","msg":"有積蓄冇咁怕<br />\n但最好就騎牛揾到馬先"},{"pid":"ca96a17cf96935d9ff31d44a0e92e0884e162933","tid":2098590,"uid":4179,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"開心最緊要 走"},{"pid":"0c0162268be9988040bcdd763e546586f581e563","tid":2098590,"uid":62565,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:01:32.000Z","msg":"空降得條友落黎做你上司 呢D公司 所謂升你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內部提升機會..  基本上都極小機會真係升你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" 