9:38.000Z","msg":"最憎話遲吓升你先依種空頭支票，講得出多數都呃尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:56:40.000Z","msg":"空頭支票真係聽得多<br />\n仲係好多人信唔敢走"},{"pid":"6ec62e4d807f749f2dcc0a4b667ce4f7ad008918","tid":2098590,"uid":34935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:58:09.000Z","msg":"好想祼辭 但冇乜積蓄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713393b19718a90c3fb628eb0e794efff6f4d511","tid":2098590,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:58:37.000Z","msg":"條命自己既<br />\n唔好理人點睇"},{"pid":"d29d3f45d96c6f47a9bffa9554565438fe96b892","tid":2098590,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5ae30dc09f56da5d46c4a79db0143ee97c5e97","tid":2098590,"uid":260603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0d2b7c5bd2937db7530c338cd5f81327b35c6a7","tid":2098590,"uid":129836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:57:10.000Z","msg":"依家份工做左一年零八個月<br />\n早幾個月空降左個男上司 面和心不和<br />\n好似磨合極大家都唔係好夾 開始有啲頂唔順<br />\n<br />\n同team有個同事都係因為佢 上個月走咗<br />\n聽佢講見到廿鳩幾份工 仲係未有著落<br />\n我都諗咗幾個月 望住依家失業率咁高真係好卻步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日諗住肺炎好快過 個市好返啲就可以走<br />\n拖下拖下終於到咗頂唔順嘅一刻 肺炎又未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早兩個禮拜老細搵我吹水 話諗住我做夠兩年就升我<br />\n我仲半信半疑緊 覺得佢係驚冇人幫佢做嘢先用呢招氹我<br />\n聽返有幾個同事都係話會升最後都冇升 等下等下就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有幾個月先夠兩年 但係我好似忍唔到咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家辭職 係咪好on9？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:14:55.000Z","msg":"搵到就走，完<br />\n返工唔講唔講心？<br />\n唔好玩啦<br />\n佢冇咗你唔掂就自然會比多啲錢請你㗎啦"},{"pid":"7942816eb0d72b56f2f8c772ba0ec3d62a778346","tid":2098590,"uid":164509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:16:12.000Z","msg":"呢個時候要能伸能屈. 你上司無權炒你，洗乜自己先放棄. 呢個時期唔好裸辭."},{"pid":"c369c6154dddb06d285bad6fbbf7710c16c415b1","tid":2098590,"uid":243175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:21:52.000Z","msg":"仲返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食老綜啦"},{"pid":"e793eea53a8378560ac55a44ad423eb74527ba44","tid":2098590,"uid":22069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:23:48.000Z","msg":"升你=呃鳩你"},{"pid":"14a42ff323957beae359ee3699b920e5fb282f81","tid":2098590,"uid":129836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3526a04c905c6e2d6d47e86f37bfc4a1aa2f157b","tid":2098590,"uid":22010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T23:24:57.000Z","msg":"做得勁唔開心 份工唔岩我做 <br />\n一晚札醒兩次 岩岩訓醒個腦勁空蕩<br />\n又怕到時reference check比佢唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:25:44.000Z","msg":"我都會 每個星期日到夜晚就會好驚好驚<br />\n每日返工倒數星期五<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c8bfa48c44b9bee30df2f2b5cd17061e33d4de","tid":2098590,"uid":22010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14a42ff323957beae359ee3699b920e5fb282f81","tid":2098590,"uid":129836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3526a04c905c6e2d6d47e86f37bfc4a1aa2f157b","tid":2098590,"uid":22010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T23:24:57.000Z","msg":"做得勁唔開心 份工唔岩我做 <br />\n一晚札醒兩次 岩岩訓醒個腦勁空蕩<br />\n又怕到時reference check比佢唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:25:44.000Z","msg":"我都會 每個星期日到夜晚就會好驚好驚<br />\n每日返工倒數星期五<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:26:18.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我想裸辭"},{"pid":"f48b50d0e99690721e08a6b537d2a5e1c12282f6","tid":2098590,"uid":129836,"like":0,"d